headline: Is Morgan Stanley Still Attractive After Its 41.8% 2025 Surge?
summary: Wondering if Morgan Stanley is still a buy after such a strong run, or if the upside has mostly been priced in already? This breakdown will help you decide. The stock has climbed 11.9% over the last month and 41.8% year to date, adding to an impressive 47.4% gain over the past year and 204.9% over five years, even with a modest 0.8% dip in the last week.
